value.zh:
示例 \xx [PATTERN] obj

\d  [PATTERN] 对象
\dn [PATTERN] 模式
\db [PATTERN] 表空间
\l  [PATTERN] 数据库
\du [PATTERN] 用户
\dt [PATTERN] 表
\di [PATTERN] 索引
\ds [PATTERN] 序列
\df [PATTERN] 函数
\dv [PATTERN] 视图
如果表达式[PATTERN]为空，就显示当前库当前模式下的所有；
如果表达式为*，则显示所有库模式下的所有；
其他的都是根据表达式匹配对应的名称。
最大数量：最多查询结果集
最大行：单个结果集查询数据行数
value.en:
example \xx [PATTERN] obj

\d  [PATTERN] Object
\dn [PATTERN] Schema
\db [PATTERN] Table Space
\l  [PATTERN] Database
\du [PATTERN] User
\dt [PATTERN] Table
\di [PATTERN] Index
\ds [PATTERN] Sequence
\df [PATTERN] Function
\dv [PATTERN] View
If the expression [pattern] is empty, all data in the current schema of the current library will be displayed;
If the expression is *, all data in all library schemas will be displayed;
The others match the corresponding name according to the expression.
MaxSet: the maximum number of query result sets
MaxRow: the maximum number of rows of query data in a single result set
